964
01:09:25,119 --> 01:09:27,746
[Female psychiatrist, in French]

965
01:10:13,293 --> 01:10:15,294
ALGERIAN MAN: Valentina.

966
01:10:16,629 --> 01:10:18,338
FEMALE PSYCHIATRIST:
Valentina.

967
01:10:18,423 --> 01:10:19,923
