[Algerian man, in French]

986
01:15:50,046 --> 01:15:51,463
[Gasps]

987
01:15:53,966 --> 01:15:55,383
<i>Pardon.</i>

988
01:16:05,394 --> 01:16:06,478
Problem?

989
01:16:28,042 --> 01:16:29,501
<i>Attendez.</i>

990
01:16:30,544 --> 01:16:32,045
<i>Voilà.</i>

991
