1002
01:19:23,926 --> 01:19:25,844
- Yellow.
- Yellow.

1003
01:19:25,928 --> 01:19:27,429
- Year.
- Year.

1004
01:19:27,513 --> 01:19:28,888
- Yet.
- Yet.

1005
01:19:28,973 --> 01:19:30,682
- Yesterday.
- Yesterday.

1006
01:19:30,766 --> 01:19:33,685
- Yoke.
