[In Russian]

1018
01:22:00,541 --> 01:22:02,083
[Sacha in Russian]

1019
01:22:15,014 --> 01:22:17,932
MAN, on tape:
Remember, when two vowels go walking,

1020
01:22:18,017 --> 01:22:20,143
